vote.title:
A public hearing to receive comments regarding an application for and an ordinance granting a Planned Development District for MC-4 Multiple Commercial District uses and single family uses on property zoned an MC-4 Multiple Commercial District, on the southwest corner of Skillman Street and Whitehurst Drive
Recommendation of Staff:  Denial without prejudice
Recommendation of CPC:  Approval, subject to a conceptual plan and conditions
Z201-162(LG)
